         lua-yaml,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: lua libs for ngcp-klish-config
 This package provides the lua ngcp lib that ngcp-klish-config
 uses.

Package: ngcp-templates-ce-klish
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
