Description: Configuration templates for NGCP Klish/Clish
 Configuration templates for Klish/Clish management of
 NGCP services. This package is part of NGCP platform's
 configuration framework.
 .
 This package provides the configuration files for the
 Sipwise sip:provider Community Edition (CE).

